&lt;h3&gt;


  The Game-Changer: Agents.md
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I started by creating an &lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;Agents.md&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; document ‚Äî a comprehensive "contract" that defined:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚úÖ Tech stack: Java 1.8, Spring Boot 2.7.18, NO frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚úÖ Architecture rules: layer dependencies, module structure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚úÖ Prohibited technologies: TypeScript, Angular, React, npm, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
